Northam Halts All Underground Tramming at Zondereinde After Worker Killed

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-08T07:22:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/northam-halts-all-underground-tramming-at-zondereinde-after-worker-killed.html
Northam Platinum Ltd. (NHM)  said it has
stopped underground tramming operations at its Zondereinde mine
in  South Africa  after a worker was killed in an accident
yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  